## GetFormDataOptions.filterFields property

Cherry-pick the form fields you want. Useful in very large forms where only a few fields are required. Does \*\*not\*\* affect `additionalEntries`<!-- -->.

**Signature:**

```typescript
filterFields?: string[];
```
